Jody Lawrance https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jody_Lawrance 0 Jody Lawrance (October 19, 1930 – July 10, 1986), sometimes known by the surname Lawrence, was an American actress who starred in many Hollywood films during the 1950s through the early 1960s.
